{"word":"Locust","slug":"locust","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Locust</b> Authorized as food<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=11&verse=22'>Lev 11:22</a><br/> Used as food<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=3&verse=4'>Mat 3:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=1&verse=6'>Mar 1:6</a><br/> Plague of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=10&verse=19'>Exo 10:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=105&verse=35'>Psa 105:35</a><br/> Devastation by<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=28&verse=38'>Deu 28:38</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=8&verse=37'>1Ki 8:37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=7&verse=13'>2Ch 7:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=33&verse=4'>Isa 33:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=29&chapter=1&verse=7'>Joe 1:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=9&verse=10'>Rev 9:10</a><br/> Sun obscured by<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=29&chapter=2&verse=2'>Joe 2:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=29&chapter=2&verse=10'>Joe 2:10</a><br/> Instincts of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=30&verse=27'>Pro 30:27</a><br/> Often inaccurately translated grasshopper<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=6&verse=5'>Jdg 6:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=7&verse=12'>Jdg 7:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=39&verse=20'>Job 39:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=46&verse=23'>Jer 46:23</a><br/><a href='S:Grasshopper'>Grasshopper</a><br/> Figurative<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=46&verse=23'>Jer 46:23</a><br/> Symbolic<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=9&verse=10'>Rev 9:10</a>"}]}